data.description: Wonderful opportunity to own in highly-sought Carrollton Subdivision. This split-level home features a spacious living/dining room/kitchen combination, three bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a walk-out to the rear deck on the main level. The basement features a laundry room with a clothes washer and dryer, a half bath, an office, and access to the 2-car oversized garage. The exterior features a large, fully fenced rear yard, with a wooden deck patio, children's playhouse, and storage shed. Located just a short drive from Frederick Crossing shopping center, Costco, MARC Train Station, and major commuter routes such as I-270, I-70, and I-15.
